OL,3,CAnalysis: Trump's colossal Iran gamble
OL,4,Cis only the start
OL,6,FThere are many labels we can now bury.
OL,8,FAmerica is not isolationist.
OL,10,FThere is no America First foreign
OL,11,Fpolicy.
OL,13,FDonald Trump is not the man to end the
OL,14,F'forever wars,' despite all the
OL,15,Fpromises he made on the campaign trail.
OL,17,FInstead, we are left to contemplate a
OL,18,Funiquely impulsive and instinctive
OL,19,Fcommander-in-chief.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
