OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1772615079
OL,3,CAnalysis: Trump's colossal Iran gamble
OL,4,Cis only the start
OL,6,FThere has not been even the pretence
OL,7,Fof consulting the United Nations
OL,8,Fbefore launching the largest war in
OL,9,Fthe Middle East since 2003.
OL,11,FUnmistakably, it is a war of choice.
OL,12,FOne being waged with a single ally,
OL,13,FIsrael.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
