OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1772615079
OL,3,CAnalysis: Trump's colossal Iran gamble
OL,4,Cis only the start
OL,6,FThere has been no authorisation - or
OL,7,Feven serious engagement - with
OL,8,FCongress despite the deeply alarming
OL,9,Fimplications of launching a conflict
OL,10,Fof such risk and unpredictability.
OL,12,FAnd as for taking advice from
OL,13,Ftraditional European allies -
OL,14,Fincluding Britain - who have major
OL,15,Fcommercial and political stakes in the
OL,16,FMiddle East?
OL,18,FWell, we heard what the Secretary of
OL,19,FWar said about them at his Pentagon
OL,20,Fbriefing yesterday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1772615079
OL,3,CAnalysis: Trump's colossal Iran gamble
OL,4,Cis only the start
OL,6,FWitheringly - not even trying to hide
OL,7,Fhis contempt - Pete Hegseth called
OL,8,FAmerica's European allies "hand-
OL,9,Fwringers and pearl-clutchers."
OL,11,FSo Donald Trump, uniquely, is the
OL,12,Fowner of this war and whatever chaos
OL,13,Funfolds.
OL,15,FThe decision point for this attack was
OL,16,Fprobably 59 days ago.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
