OL,3,CAnalysis: Trump's colossal Iran gamble
OL,4,Cis only the start
OL,6,FIt was then, on January 3rd, that US
OL,7,FDelta Force troops stormed the
OL,8,Fstronghold of Nicolas Maduro and
OL,9,Fspirited the Venezuelan dictator out
OL,10,Fof the country and into a New York
OL,11,Fprison cell.
OL,13,FThe stunning success of that military
OL,14,Foperation appears to have emboldened
OL,15,FPresident Trump and persuaded him that
OL,16,Fthe US military could reshape not just
OL,17,Fthe Americas, but the world.
OL,19,FAnd looking ahead, here's the point to
OL,20,Fbear in mind.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
