CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1772615079
OL,3,CAnalysis: Trump's colossal Iran gamble
OL,4,Cis only the start
OL,6,FThe team in the White House,
OL,7,Fespecially Secretary of State and
OL,8,FNational Security Adviser Marco Rubio,
OL,9,Fhave another goal when the Iran war
OL,10,Fends.
OL,12,FThey want to take down the Cuban
OL,13,Fcommunist government. That is closest
OL,14,Fto Rubio's heart.
OL,16,FIt is possible to glimpse through the
OL,17,Fbillowing smoke over Tehran and see
OL,18,Fhow Trump wants to go down in history.
OL,20,FAs the slayer of the Venezuelan,
OL,21,FIranian, and Cuban regimes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
